variants.modifierDescription: Maximum Warframe Energy capacity is quartered. Energy Siphon is less effective.
Enemies deal increased Blast damage and also have increased Immunity to said damage type.
Eximus units have a much higher spawn rate in this mission. Some of their auras stack.
